{
  "texts": [
    "Details of excluded articles are shown in the PRISMA flow diagram 74, see Fig. 1.",
    "The full list of included RCTs is available in Supplementary Data 1.",
    "The majority of studies were conducted in China (n = 24, 37%) 12, 15, 27, 29, 30, [37] [38] [39] [40] [41] 43, [59] [60] [61] [62] [63] [64] [65] [66] 68, 69, [71] [72] [73], USA (n = 12, 18%) 16, 19, 22, 25, 28, 32, 42, 51, 55, 56, 67, 70 and Japan (n = 5, 8%) 9, 24, 31, 33, 50.",
    "There were 4 international multicentre studies conducted across European sites 11, 13, 34, 44 and 10 studies performed within individual European countries: France (n = 3) 18, 36, 58, Italy (n = 2) 53, 54, Spain (n = 2) 21, 47, England (n = 1) 26, Germany (n = 1) 48 and Denmark (n = 1) 14.",
    "The remainder (n = 10, 15%) took place across South Korea, Taiwan, India, Thailand, Israel, Mexico, Argentina, Rwanda and Malawi, as shown in Fig. 2 10, 17, 20, 23, 35, 45, 46, 49, 52, 57."
